profile: Eveque Painting is a paint company in Windsor and Essex county. We Specialize in interior painting, exterior painting, deck staining, and painting kitchen cabinets. We have painted hundreds of homes in the last 4 years. Our entire business is structured around delivering value and securing trust. Our #1 goal is to be able to get a referral and a good review from you. We look forward to being able to satisfy your needs.
